error:
============= E2E DB AUTO-START FAILED =============
Postgres is not reachable at localhost:5433, and Docker auto-start failed.
This usually means Docker Desktop is not running, or docker is not installed.

[FALLBACK OPTIONS]:
 1. Start Docker Desktop and run this command again.
 2. Manually start PostgreSQL on port 5433 with user 'hireflow' and password 'hireflow_password'.
 3. Point to an existing DB using HIREFLOW_E2E_AUTO_DB_START=false DATABASE_URL=...
====================================================
